      <div class="govspeak">
<h2 id="published-and-upcoming-statistics">Published and upcoming statistics</h2>

<p>We publish Official and National Statistics on a regular basis. They provide accurate and impartial information about Department for Work and Pensions (<abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr>) benefits and related subjects.</p>

<div class="call-to-action">
<p>Browse our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-work-pensions/about/statistics#dwp-statistics-and-contacts-by-theme">statistics by theme</a>.</p>
</div>

<p>Use search terms and filters to find <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics?keywords=&topics%5B%5D=all&departments%5B%5D=department-for-work-pensions&from_date=&to_date=">published statistics</a> and details of <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics/announcements?utf8=%E2%9C%93&organisations%5B%5D=department-for-work-pensions">upcoming statistics in our statistics release calendar</a>.</p>

<h3 id="ad-hoc-statistics">Ad hoc statistics</h3>

<p>We also publish <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/ad-hoc-statistical-publications-list">ad hoc statistics</a>. These are published in response to specific questions and are not part of our regular Official and National Statistics publications.</p>

<p>View details of our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics/list-of-scheduled-upcoming-ad-hoc-statistical-releases">upcoming ad hoc statistics</a>.</p>

<h3 id="management-information-and-ad-hoc-analyses">Management information and ad hoc analyses</h3>

<p>We also publish <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/dwp-ad-hoc-analyses">management information and ad hoc analyses</a> that are not classified as statistics (or research). These are published in the interests of transparency and are not part of our regular Official and National Statistics publications.</p>

<p>View details of our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/list-of-upcoming-releases-of-management-information-and-ad-hoc-analyses">upcoming management information and ad hoc analyses</a>.</p>

<h3 id="freedom-of-information-requests-related-to-statistics">Freedom of Information requests related to statistics</h3>

<p>We also publish our responses to <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/dwp-statistical-foi-releases">Freedom of Information requests related to <abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr> statistics</a>.</p>

<h2 id="data-analysis-tools">Data analysis tools</h2>

<p>Explore <abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr> data in more depth using our data analysis tools.</p>

<h3 id="data-visualisations">Data visualisations</h3>

<p>You can explore and customise <abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr> statistics using the following interactive data visualisations:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a rel="external" href="http://femavis.herokuapp.com/index.html">Fraud and error in the benefit system</a></li>
  <li><a rel="external" href="http://pipdash.herokuapp.com/index.html">Personal Independence Payment (<abbr title="Personal Independence Payment">PIP</abbr>)</a></li>
  <li><a rel="external" href="http://ninodash.herokuapp.com/index.html">National Insurance Number allocations to adult overseas nationals</a></li>
</ul>

<h3 id="stat-xplore">Stat-Xplore</h3>

<p><a rel="external" href="https://stat-xplore.dwp.gov.uk/">Stat-Xplore</a> is an online tool that lets you create and download customised statistical tables, and view the results in interactive charts. It currently holds statistics on:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Attendance Allowance (<abbr title="Attendance Allowance">AA</abbr>)</li>
  <li>Benefit cap</li>
  <li>Bereavement Benefits</li>
  <li>Carer’s Allowance</li>
  <li>Disability Living Allowance (<abbr title="Disability Living Allowance">DLA</abbr>)</li>
  <li>Employment and Support Allowance (<abbr title="Employment and Support Allowance">ESA</abbr>)</li>
  <li>Fraud and error in the benefit system</li>
  <li>Housing Benefit (<abbr title="Housing Benefit">HB</abbr>)</li>
  <li>National Insurance number allocations to adult overseas nationals</li>
  <li>Pension Credit</li>
  <li>Personal Independence Payment (<abbr title="Personal Independence Payment">PIP</abbr>)</li>
  <li>Sanction decisions for Jobseeker’s Allowance (<abbr title="Jobseeker’s Allowance">JSA</abbr>), Employment and Support Allowance (<abbr title="Employment and Support Allowance">ESA</abbr>), Income Support (<abbr title="Income Support">IS</abbr>) and Universal Credit (<abbr title="Universal Credit">UC</abbr>)</li>
  <li>State Pension</li>
  <li>Universal Credit</li>
  <li>Widow’s Benefit</li>
  <li>Work Programme</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="changes-to-dwp-statistical-geographies">Changes to <abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr> statistical geographies</h2>

<p>Due to increasing demand from users, <abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr> is making improvements to the published geography information in its National and Official statistics releases. This includes data released on <a rel="external" href="https://stat-xplore.dwp.gov.uk/">Stat-Xplore</a>. Read our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/dwp-statistical-geographies-in-national-and-official-statistics"><abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr> statistical geographies note</a> for more information about the changes.</p>

