<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/income-support-lone-parent-regime-figures-on-sanctions-and-work-focused-interviews--2">Income Support lone parent regime</a> – This statistical series has ended. The statistics are now included in our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/dwp-statistical-summaries">benefits statistical summaries</a> and <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/jobseekers-allowance-sanctions">benefit sanctions statistics</a>.</p>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics/lone-parents-receiving-jsa-monthly-claimant-count">Lone parents receiving Jobseeker’s Allowance</a> – Number of lone parents receiving <abbr title="Jobseeker’s Allowance">JSA</abbr>.  <br></br>
Contact: <a href="mailto:alan.gibson@dwp.gov.uk">alan.gibson@dwp.gov.uk</a>, 0191 216 2804</p>

