Contact: <a href="mailto:alan.gibson@dwp.gov.uk">alan.gibson@dwp.gov.uk</a>, 0191 216 2804</p>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/social-justice-outcomes-framework-family-stability-indicator">Social Justice outcomes framework: family stability indicator</a> – Family stability indicator results.  <br></br>
