<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/pre-work-programme-and-get-britain-working#new-enterprise-allowance">New Enterprise Allowance (<abbr title="New Enterprise Allowance">NEA</abbr>)</a> – Statistics on <abbr title="New Enterprise Allowance">NEA</abbr> including number of starts with a business mentor and the number of business starts.  <br></br>
