<h2 id="policies-and-procedures-for-dwp-statistics">Policies and procedures for <abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr> statistics</h2>
<p>We’ve published our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/dwp-statistics-policies-and-procedures">policies and procedures for <abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr> statistics</a> in the interests of transparency and to comply with the <abbr title="United Kingdom">UK</abbr> Statistics Authority code of practice.</p>

<h2 id="pre-release-access-to-statistics">Pre-release access to statistics</h2>
<p>We’ve published the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics/pre-release-access-to-statistics-order-2008"><abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr> arrangements for pre-release access to statistics</a> in the interests of openness and transparency. This provides details of  the job titles of everyone who has pre-release access and the organisations to which they belong.</p>

